    • Field Detail

      • EPOCH_TIME

        public static final long EPOCH_TIME
        Base time to be used for storing time values as diffs (int) rather than full blown epoch based vals (long) This allows for a space in seconds, of roughly 68 years. Reference value (1514764800000) - Monday, January 1, 2018 12:00:00 AM The fixed time in the past (instead of System.currentTimeMillis() prevents any time discrepancies among nodes, mis-translated as diffs of -1 ie. Record.NOT_AVAILABLE values. (see. https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast-enterprise/issues/2527)
